description: Available at: https://openstudionetwork.com/keezer - So you've played all the way through to the final bars of a tune, but now what? In bands, more often than not, it's the piano player's job to come up with an ending. In this 2-part lesson, Geoffrey demonstrates a myriad of traditional and not-so-traditional ways to conclude a song. Great for guitarists too! (Level: Intermediate)
